(2, 'WHAT IS HARD WATER', 'Where Can It Be Seen?', 'Hard water contains high levels of minerals like calcium and magnesium, which can cause scaling, discoloration, and the deterioration of household appliances. It can also lead to dry skin, dull hair, and stained laundry.', 'B.png', 3),
